\c 9
\s Dhavhidhi anovonga nokuti
\s Jehovha akamurwira
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; neMutirabheni. Pisarema raDhavhidhi. Ndichavonga Jehovha nomwoyo wangu wose; Ndichaparidza mabasa enyu ose anoshamisa.
\v 2 Ndichafara nokukufarirai zvikuru; Ndichaimbira zita renyu nziyo dzokurumbidza, imi Wokumusorosoro.
\v 3 Kana vavengi vangu vachidzokera shure, Vanogumburwa nokupera pamberi penyu.
\v 4 Nokuti mandiruramisira mhosva yangu; Makagara pachigaro choushe muchitonga nokururama.
\v 5 Makatuka vahedheni, makaparadza vakaipa, Makadzima zita ravo nokusingaperi-peri.
\v 6 Vavengi vakapera, vakaparadzwa nokusingaperi; Makaparadza maguta avo, Nechiyeudzo chawo chakaparara.
\v 7 Asi Jehovha agere ari mambo nokusingaperi; Akagadzira chigaro chake choushe kuti atonge.
\v 8 Achatonga nyika nokururama, Achatonga vanhu zvakafanira.
\v 9 Jehovha achava nhare yakasimba kuna vanomanikidzwa, Nhare yakasimba panguva yokutambudzika.
\v 10 Vanoziva zita renyu vachavimba nemi; Nokuti imi Jehovha hamuna kurasha vanokutsvakai.
\v 11 Imbirai Jehovha nziyo dzokumurumbidza, iye agere paZioni; dudzirai zvaakaita pakati pendudzi dzavanhu.
\v 12 Nokuti iye, anotsiva ropa, anovarangarira; Haakanganwi kuchema kwavarombo.
\v 13 Ndinzwirei tsitsi, Jehovha; Tarirai, kumanikidzwa kwangu
\s navanondivenga,
\s Imi munondisimudza pamisuo
\s yorufu;
\p
\v 14 Kuti ndiparidze kurumbidzwa
\s kwenyu kwose;
\s Pamisuo yomukunda welioni, Ndichafarira kuponesa kwenyu.
\p
\v 15 Vahedheni vakanyura mugomba ravakachera;
\s Rutsoka rwavo rwakabatwa mumumbure, wavakavanza.
\p
\v 16 Jehovha wakazvizivisa, akatonga; Akaipa wakateyiwa nebasa
\s ramaoko ake.
\p
\v 17 Vakaipa vachadzokera kuSheori,
\s Ivo vahedheni vose, vakakanganwa Mwari.
\p
\v 18 Nokuti anoshaiwa haangakanganikwi nokusingaperi,
\s Nokutarira kwomurombo hakungaperi nokusingaperi.
\p
\v 19 Simukai Jehovha; munhu ngaarege kukunda;
\s Vahedheni ngavatongwe pamberi penyu.
\p
\v 2 Â° Chivatyisai, Jehovha; Vahedheni ngavazive kuti vanongova vanhu.
